name: SlingYeet
description:
Click and drag the blue Godot icon and release to send it flying at incoming meteors.

5 waves, 30 seconds each. 3 Health points. Keep the meteors from touching the bottom. 

A simple learning project in Godot 4. Please excuse the name, I could not think of anything better.

Art: Void Environment Pack by FoozleCC

Music: Nowhere Land - Kevin Macleod
